'''Ishyamba rya Mukura'''  ni ishyamba riherereye mu gice cy'amajyaruguru y'uburengerazuba bw'U  [[Rwanda]], hangana na kilometero 1.200 km 2  ishyamba rya Mukura  riri mu burengerazuba bw'u Rwanda  mu karere ka Rustiro, rikaba mu gace kamajyaruguru ya congo . ni Rimwe mu gice cy’amashyamba y’imisozi yakomotse kuri  [[Pariki ya Nyungwe|Nyungwe]] agakura kugera muri Parike y’ibirunga,  ubu Mukura ni agace k’ishyamba konyine. 

Mukura yagizwe ishyamba rya kimeza muri 1951. Ubusanzwe yari ifite ubuso bwa hegitari 30.000. Ariko, hafi kimwe cya kabiri  cy' ishyamba ndetse n'urugaga rw'ibinyabuzima rwarazimiye kuburyo ubu hasigaye hegitari  ha 16.000 gusa.  Ibintu byinshi byatumye igabanuka, harimo ubucucike bwabaturage bagera kuri 600 kuri km 2 hamwe n’amafaranga biinjiza mu rugo angana na $ 3 / ukwezi, ibi bigatuma abaturage bakoresha ishyamba mu buryo butemewe kugirango babone imibereho n'amafaranga.

Ubushyuhe bwa buri mwaka bw’ishyamba rya Mukura ni 15 ° C. Ishyamba ryazamutse kugera ku burebure bwa metero 2600 hejuru y’inyanja, kandi ryakira 1500&nbsp;mm y'imvura buri mwaka. 

Iri shyamba rigira amoko y’inyoni agera kuri 163. 

